<button class="accordion">Why is writing necessary in healthcare?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Writing makes people better doctors because it increases their ability to be good observers. They start to pay attention to details. If they're writing about a patient, we encourage them to notice not only what the patient looks like, but ask, what are the sounds around the patient.</p>
