<button class="accordion">How can you effectively communicate with patients and visitors during times of need?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Ways to communicate with patients and visitors:</p>
<li>Announce your presence</li>
<li>Welcome the patient</li>
<li>Ask if there's anything the patient needs</li>
<li>Review what was done and explain when the next service will be</li>
<li>Exit with a kind word.</li><p></p>
</div>
